    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "You're not entirely wrong; there are some tasks where it's *helpful*... but I wouldn't say it's always needed or should be enabled by default -- personally.\r\n\r\nIn general, I think it more valuable for PS modules to be *consistent*, but... that's a personal opinion of mine, so if you have something you feel it's needed for, go for it. ðŸ˜„ ",
